title: Bobby’s Girlfriend Followed On Her Run + Raymundo Writes Wedding Song For Fiancé + Travis Denning Celebrates First #1 Song
itunes:title: Bobby’s Girlfriend Followed On Her Run + Raymundo Writes Wedding Song For Fiancé + Travis Denning Celebrates First #1 Song
description:
Bobby and his girlfriend have both started running outside. He talks about her recently being followed while out for a jog by herself. Raymundo debuts a song he wrote for his fiance for their upcoming October wedding. Plus, we talk to Travis Denning about his record-breaking #1 song!
